{"id": "7eed730a-eb15-48ba-992f-ea0c56c3f610", "rules": {}, "module": "crm", "status": "applied", "version": 1, "form_type": "simple", "semantics": {"domain": "operations", "keywords": ["partner", "strategic", "alliance", "referral"], "description": "Strategic partners and referral organizations.", "example_questions": ["List strategic partners", "Show alliance records", "Find referral partners"]}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-01-24T05:03:06.997383+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T06:22:31.728987+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "crm.contacts", "entity_type": "partners", "dependencies": ["external.contacts", "external.accounts", "external.user_account_assignments"], "display_name": null, "jsonb_schema": null, "physical_ddl": null, "ai_resolution": "direct", "entity_schema": "crm", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "master", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW external.v_partners AS 
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone, uc.lifecycle_stage, uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload, uc.details, 
    ec.account_id, ec.is_partner_delegate, ec.is_primary, ec.company, ec.tags, ec.last_contacted_at, ec.last_engaged_at, 
    a.name AS partner_company, a.domain, a.industry, 
    ua.user_id AS assigned_internal_user, ua.role_in_assignment, ua.functional_role, 
    uc.created_at, uc.updated_at 
FROM unified.contacts uc 
LEFT JOIN external.contacts ec ON ec.id = uc.id 
LEFT JOIN external.accounts a ON a.id = ec.account_id 
LEFT JOIN external.user_account_assignments ua ON ua.account_id = ec.account_id 
WHERE uc.contact_type = 'external' AND uc.lifecycle_stage = 'partner';
        ", "partition_filter": "contact_type = 'external' AND lifecycle_stage = 'partner'"}

    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS external.contacts (
      id uuid NOT NULL DEFAULT extensions.uuid_generate_v4(),
      name text NOT NULL,
      email text NULL,
      phone text NULL,
      created_at timestamp with time zone NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
      updated_at timestamp with time zone NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
      account_id uuid NULL,
      is_primary boolean NULL DEFAULT false,
      details jsonb NULL DEFAULT '{}'::jsonb,
      organization_id uuid NULL DEFAULT '55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555'::uuid,
      location_id uuid NULL,
      lifecycle_stage public.lifecycle_stage NULL DEFAULT 'lead'::lifecycle_stage,
      operational_status text NULL DEFAULT 'NEW'::text,
      contact_type text NULL DEFAULT 'standard'::text,
      is_partner_delegate boolean NULL DEFAULT false,
      lead_source text NULL,
      score numeric NULL DEFAULT 0,
      company text NULL,
      industry text NULL,
      tags text[] NULL DEFAULT '{}'::text[],
      last_contacted_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      communication_preferences jsonb NULL DEFAULT '{}'::jsonb,
      deleted_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      source_lead_id uuid NULL,
      source_customer_id uuid NULL,
      entity_instance_id uuid NULL,
      persona_type text NULL,
      linkedin_url text NULL,
      last_engaged_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      CONSTRAINT contacts_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id),
      CONSTRAINT contacts_email_key UNIQUE (email),
      CONSTRAINT contacts_entity_instance_id_key UNIQUE (entity_instance_id)
      -- NOTE: FK to accounts is handled in extra_objects or later migration to avoid circular dependencies
    );

{"id": "7eed730a-eb15-48ba-992f-ea0c56c3f610", "rules": {}, "module": "crm", "status": "applied", "version": 1, "form_type": "simple", "semantics": {"domain": "operations", "keywords": ["partner", "strategic", "alliance", "referral"], "description": "Strategic partners and referral organizations.", "example_questions": ["List strategic partners", "Show alliance records", "Find referral partners"]}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-01-24T05:03:06.997383+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T06:22:31.728987+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "crm.contacts", "entity_type": "partners", "dependencies": ["external.contacts", "external.accounts", "external.user_account_assignments"], "display_name": null, "jsonb_schema": null, "physical_ddl": null, "ai_resolution": "direct", "entity_schema": "crm", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "master", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW external.v_partners AS 
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone, uc.lifecycle_stage, uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload, uc.details, 
    ec.account_id, ec.is_partner_delegate, ec.is_primary, ec.company, ec.tags, ec.last_contacted_at, ec.last_engaged_at, 
    a.name AS partner_company, a.domain, a.industry, 
    ua.user_id AS assigned_internal_user, ua.role_in_assignment, ua.functional_role, 
    uc.created_at, uc.updated_at 
FROM unified.contacts uc 
LEFT JOIN external.contacts ec ON ec.id = uc.id 
LEFT JOIN external.accounts a ON a.id = ec.account_id 
LEFT JOIN external.user_account_assignments ua ON ua.account_id = ec.account_id 
WHERE uc.contact_type = 'external' AND uc.lifecycle_stage = 'partner';
        ", "partition_filter": "contact_type = 'external' AND lifecycle_stage = 'partner'"}

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW hr.v_contractors AS
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone,
    uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload,
    ou.location_id, ou.manager_id, ou.user_id,

LEFT JOIN hr.workers w ON w.id = uc.id

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW hr.v_consultants AS
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone,
    uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload,
    ou.location_id, ou.manager_id, ou.user_id,
    u.pref_organization_id AS primary_org,
    w.details AS hr_details,
    w.details->'employment'->>'hireDate' AS contract_start,
    w.details->'employment'->>'jobTitle' AS role_title,
    uc.created_at, uc.updated_at
FROM unified.contacts uc
LEFT JOIN identity.organization_users ou ON ou.id = uc.id
LEFT JOIN identity.users u ON u.id = ou.user_id
LEFT JOIN hr.workers w ON w.id = uc.id
WHERE uc.contact_type = 'worker' AND uc.persona_type = 'consultant';
        ", "partition_filter": "contact_type = 'worker' AND persona_type = 'consultant'", "ui_details_overview": {}}

{"id": "7eed730a-eb15-48ba-992f-ea0c56c3f610", "rules": {}, "module": "external", "status": "applied", "version": 1, "semantics": {"domain": "operations", "keywords": ["partner", "strategic", "alliance", "referral"], "description": "Strategic partners and referral organizations.", "example_questions": ["List strategic partners", "Show alliance records", "Find referral partners"]}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-01-24T05:03:06.997383+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T06:22:31.728987+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "unified.contacts", "entity_type": "partners", "dependencies": ["external.contacts", "external.accounts", "external.user_account_assignments"], "display_name": null, "physical_ddl": null, "entity_schema": "external", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "master", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW external.v_partners AS 
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone, uc.lifecycle_stage, uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload, uc.details, 
    ec.account_id, ec.is_partner_delegate, ec.is_primary, ec.company, ec.tags, ec.last_contacted_at, ec.last_engaged_at, 
    a.name AS partner_company, a.domain, a.industry, 
    ua.user_id AS assigned_internal_user, ua.role_in_assignment, ua.functional_role, 
    uc.created_at, uc.updated_at 
FROM unified.contacts uc 
LEFT JOIN external.contacts ec ON ec.id = uc.id 
LEFT JOIN external.accounts a ON a.id = ec.account_id 
LEFT JOIN external.user_account_assignments ua ON ua.account_id = ec.account_id 
WHERE uc.contact_type = 'external' AND uc.lifecycle_stage = 'partner';
        ", "partition_filter": "contact_type = 'external' AND lifecycle_stage = 'partner'"}

{"id": "49c40410-019a-4254-8e13-5166f7a729b8", "rules": {}, "module": "hr", "status": "draft", "version": 1, "form_type": "nested", "semantics": {"resolution": {"dependents": [{"key": "items", "table": "workforce.expense_sheet_items", "fk_column": "expense_sheet_id"}]}}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-02-07T04:30:53.124112+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T05:40:27.301125+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "workforce.expense_sheets", "entity_type": "expense_sheets", "dependencies": null, "display_name": null, "jsonb_schema": null, "physical_ddl": null, "ai_resolution": "nested_create", "entity_schema": "workforce", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "transactional", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
SELECT 
    base.id,
    base.organization_id,
    base.user_id,
    base.expensesheet_date,
    base.last_date,
    base.grand_total,
    base.status,
    base.stage_id,
    base.display_id,
    base.automation_bp_instance_id,
    base.automation_esm_instance_id,
    base.created_at,
    base.updated_at,
    base.created_by,
    base.updated_by,
    fk_org.name AS organization_display,
    fk_user.name AS user_display,
    (SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object(
        'id', esi.id,
        'expense_type_id', esi.expense_type_id,
        'item_date', esi.item_date,
        'amount', esi.amount,
        'description', esi.description
    )) FROM workforce.expense_sheet_items esi WHERE esi.expense_sheet_id = base.id) AS items
FROM workforce.expense_sheets base
LEFT JOIN identity.organizations fk_org ON base.organization_id = fk_org.id
LEFT JOIN identity.users fk_user ON base.user_id = fk_user.id
", "partition_filter": null}

{"id": "81ebfe94-3932-4468-b7f9-ae2a2373122f", "rules": {}, "module": "external", "status": "applied", "version": 1, "form_type": "simple", "semantics": {"domain": "crm", "keywords": ["contact", "person", "email", "phone"], "description": "External business contacts and individuals.", "example_questions": ["List external contacts", "Find contacts by email", "Show contact info for a company"]}, "ui_config": {"default_view": "tableview"}, "created_at": "2026-01-11T10:57:42.249686+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T06:22:31.728987+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "unified.contacts", "entity_type": "contacts", "dependencies": ["external.contacts"], "display_name": null, "jsonb_schema": null, "physical_ddl": "
    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS external.contacts (
      id uuid NOT NULL DEFAULT extensions.uuid_generate_v4(),
      name text NOT NULL,
      email text NULL,
      phone text NULL,
      created_at timestamp with time zone NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
      updated_at timestamp with time zone NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
      account_id uuid NULL,
      is_primary boolean NULL DEFAULT false,
      details jsonb NULL DEFAULT '{}'::jsonb,
      organization_id uuid NULL DEFAULT '55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555'::uuid,
      location_id uuid NULL,
      lifecycle_stage public.lifecycle_stage NULL DEFAULT 'lead'::lifecycle_stage,
      operational_status text NULL DEFAULT 'NEW'::text,
      contact_type text NULL DEFAULT 'standard'::text,
      is_partner_delegate boolean NULL DEFAULT false,
      lead_source text NULL,
      score numeric NULL DEFAULT 0,
      company text NULL,
      industry text NULL,
      tags text[] NULL DEFAULT '{}'::text[],
      last_contacted_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      communication_preferences jsonb NULL DEFAULT '{}'::jsonb,
      deleted_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      source_lead_id uuid NULL,
      source_customer_id uuid NULL,
      entity_instance_id uuid NULL,
      persona_type text NULL,
      linkedin_url text NULL,
      last_engaged_at timestamp with time zone NULL,
      CONSTRAINT contacts_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id),
      CONSTRAINT contacts_email_key UNIQUE (email),
      CONSTRAINT contacts_entity_instance_id_key UNIQUE (entity_instance_id)
      -- NOTE: FK to accounts is handled in extra_objects or later migration to avoid circular dependencies
    );
    ", "entity_schema": "external", "extra_objects": ["CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_contacts_lifecycle_stage ON external.contacts (lifecycle_stage)", "CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_contacts_org_lifecycle ON external.contacts (organization_id, lifecycle_stage)", "CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_contacts_tags ON external.contacts USING gin (tags)", "CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_contacts_deleted_at ON external.contacts (deleted_at) WHERE (deleted_at IS NOT NULL)", "CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_contacts_universal_timeline ON external.contacts (organization_id, created_at DESC, id) INCLUDE (id, created_at)", "CREATE TRIGGER update_contacts_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON external.contacts FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column()", "ALTER TABLE external.contacts ADD CONSTRAINT contacts_account_id_fkey FOREIGN KEY (account_id) REFERENCES external.accounts (id) ON DELETE CASCADE"], "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "master", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": null, "partition_filter": "module = 'external'", "ai_resolution_strategy": "direct"}

{"id": "630086d7-d0f4-44be-b5b2-fd9be73cee2a", "rules": {}, "module": "hr", "status": "applied", "version": 4, "form_type": "simple", "semantics": {"context": {"title": "Contractors", "module": "hr", "status": "applied"}}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-01-24T05:03:06.997383+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "ui_general": {"default_view": "kanbanview", "global_actions": [{"form": "contractors_form", "label": "New"}], "available_views": ["tableview", "gridview", "detailview", "kanbanview", "metricsview"]}, "updated_at": "2026-02-09T15:42:13.348987+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "unified.contacts", "entity_type": "contractors", "dependencies": ["identity.organization_users", "hr.workers"], "display_name": null, "jsonb_schema": null, "physical_ddl": null, "ui_dashboard": {}, "ai_resolution": "direct", "entity_schema": "hr", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "transactional", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW hr.v_contractors AS
SELECT 
    uc.id, uc.organization_id, uc.display_id, uc.name, uc.email, uc.phone,
    uc.persona_type, uc.status, uc.vertical, uc.vertical_payload,
    ou.location_id, ou.manager_id, ou.user_id,
    w.details AS hr_details,
    w.details->'employment'->>'hireDate' AS contract_start,
    w.details->'employment'->>'jobTitle' AS role_title,
    uc.created_at, uc.updated_at
FROM unified.contacts uc
LEFT JOIN identity.organization_users ou ON ou.id = uc.id
LEFT JOIN hr.workers w ON w.id = uc.id
WHERE uc.contact_type = 'worker' AND uc.persona_type = 'contractor';

{"id": "1c019bb9-3fd3-4a40-9a80-745a471d09c9", "rules": {}, "module": "hr", "status": "draft", "version": 1, "semantics": {}, "ui_config": {}, "created_at": "2026-02-07T04:30:53.124112+00:00", "sub_panels": [], "updated_at": "2026-02-07T05:14:57.649242+00:00", "ai_metadata": {"embedding_model": "text-embedding-3-large"}, "base_source": "workforce.timesheets", "entity_type": "timesheets", "dependencies": null, "display_name": null, "physical_ddl": null, "entity_schema": "workforce", "extra_objects": {}, "blueprint_hash": null, "classification": "transactional", "display_format": null, "custom_view_sql": "
SELECT 
    base.id,
    base.organization_id,
    base.user_id,
    base.timesheet_date,
    base.last_date,
    base.timesheet_type,
    base.total_hours,
    base.project_details_legacy,
    base.approver_details_legacy,
    base.status,
    base.stage_id,
    base.display_id,
    base.automation_bp_instance_id,
    base.automation_esm_instance_id,
    base.created_at,
    base.updated_at,
    base.created_by,
    base.updated_by,
    fk_org.name AS organization_display,
    fk_user.name AS user_display,
    (SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object(
        'id', ti.id,
        'project_id', ti.project_id,
        'entry_date', ti.entry_date,
        'hours_worked', ti.hours_worked,
        'description', ti.description
    )) FROM workforce.timesheet_items ti WHERE ti.timesheet_id = base.id) AS items
FROM workforce.timesheets base
LEFT JOIN identity.organizations fk_org ON base.organization_id = fk_org.id
LEFT JOIN identity.users fk_user ON base.user_id = fk_user.id
", "partition_filter": null}
